ding_size":9,"heading_tag":"h2","heading_style":"none","caption_size":1.6,"caption_style":"none","link_size":1.8,"color_scheme":"option-2","margin_spacing":"negative","margin_top":0,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"ignore_spacing":false}},"info_cards":{"type":"info-cards","blocks":{"infocard_1":{"type":"infocard","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/TartCherryPowder-Organic.jpg","hide_image":false,"product":"","caption":"Pure Ingredients.","title":"Organic by Nature. Honest by Choice.","text":"<p>At Divine Ingredients, we believe nourishment shouldn’t demand compromise. That’s why every powder, herb, and spice we offer is <strong>100% organic<\/strong>, responsibly sourced, and free from synthetic nasties. We partner with eco-conscious farmers to nurture soil, communities, and flavor — because quality should radiate from farm to cup.<\/p><p>We’re not about fillers or fluff: our blends contain no preservatives, artificial dyes, or synthetic flavorings — just pure plant power in its cleanest form. For those with sensitivities, we uphold rigorous standards to keep our products allergy-safe and broadly accessible.<\/p><p>What sets us apart?<\/p><ul><li>Certified-organic, farm-to-kitchen ingredients<br\/><\/li><li>Zero artificial additives or preservatives<br\/><\/li><li>Transparency & quality testing for allergen safety<br\/><\/li><li>Sustainable sourcing for people and planet<\/li><\/ul><p>Fuel your ritual with Divine Ingredients — pure, potent, and made to elevate your daily dose of wellness.<\/p>","link_label":"","link":"","infocards_background_color":"#d4c4d9","infocards_color":"#1d1d1d"}},"infocard_2":{"type":"infocard","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/GT.Peachgo1_65ffc7e5-b64c-4c4a-a9e7-759a0e2e792e.jpg","hide_image":false,"product":"","caption":"Organic Origins.","title":"Clean Ingredients. Divine Results.","text":"<p>At Divine Ingredients, we embrace the power of plants to nourish your body with pure, organic goodness. Our powders, herbs, and botanicals are thoughtfully sourced and minimally processed—just the way nature intended.<\/p><p>We skip the fillers, refined sugars, and synthetic additives so you get only what your body needs—and nothing you don’t. Every product is clean, potent, and made with integrity, supporting your wellness journey with ingredients you can actually recognize.<\/p><p>Whether you're blending a superfood smoothie or crafting a tea ritual, our products deliver simple, plant-powered nutrition that feels as good as it tastes.<\/p><p><strong>Why Choose Divine?<\/strong><br\/><br\/>• 100% Organic & Plant-Based Ingredients<br\/><br\/>• No Artificial Additives or Preservatives<br\/><br\/>• Minimal, Transparent Ingredient Lists<br\/><br\/>• Pure, Functional Products That Work<\/p><p>Choose Divine for organic wellness you can trust—clean, conscious, and always rooted in nature.<\/p>","link_label":"","link":"","infocards_background_color":"#eae6e6","infocards_color":"#1d1d1d"}},"infocard_3":{"type":"infocard","settings":{"hide_image":true,"product":"golden-pineapple-oolong-tea","caption":"Clean Foods.","title":"Vegan. Soy Free. Low Sugar.","text":"<p>At Divine Ingredients, we believe eating well should be easy, intentional, and good for both you and the planet. That’s why our entire collection of organic powders, herbs, and botanicals is 100% plant-based, vegan-friendly, and crafted without compromise.<\/p><p>Our ingredients are naturally soy-free and thoughtfully selected to be gentle on digestion—without giving up flavor or function. With no added sugars or synthetic sweeteners, our powders offer clean, sustained energy you can feel good about.<\/p><p>From smoothie blends to nourishing tea rituals, Divine Ingredients fits seamlessly into your lifestyle. Every product is created with your wellness in mind, supporting balance, energy, and honest nourishment.<\/p><p><strong>Why Choose Divine?<\/strong><br\/><br\/>• 100% Vegan & Plant-Based Ingredients<br\/><br\/>• Soy-Free and Easy on Digestion<br\/><br\/>• No Added Sugars or Artificial Sweeteners<br\/><br\/>• Clean, Functional, and Flavorful<\/p><p>Rooted in nature, made for your everyday rituals.<\/p>","link_label":"","link":"","infocards_background_color":"#e9daec","infocards_color":"#1d1d1d"}},"infocard_4":{"type":"infocard","settings":{"hide_image":true,"product":"organic-cinnamon-spice","caption":"Simply Wholesome","title":"Naturally Delicious. Pure Ingredients.","text":"<p><br\/>At Divine Ingredients, we keep things simple—because simple is powerful. Our collection of organic powders, teas, herbs, and botanicals delivers clean, honest nutrition you can feel good about every day.<br\/><br\/>Crafted with pure, minimally processed ingredients, each product is thoughtfully balanced to support natural energy and rich, authentic flavor. No synthetic additives, no unnecessary fillers—just real plant-based goodness that fits effortlessly into your daily rituals.<br\/><br\/>Divine’s Commitment to Quality:<br\/>• Wholesome Ingredients: Pure and simple, with no artificial additives<br\/>• Balanced Flavor: Just the right amount of natural sweetness, when used<br\/>• Everyday Goodness: Made for real life, with nutrition you can trust<br\/><br\/>Simply nourishing. Naturally vibrant. Always Divine.<br\/><br\/><br\/><\/p>","link_label":"","link":"","infocards_background_color":"#f2f2f2","infocards_color":"#1d1d1d"}}},"block_order":["infocard_1","infocard_2","infocard_3","infocard_4"],"settings":{"full_width":false,"color_scheme":"","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"ignore_spacing":false,"cards_style":"style-2","margin_spacing":"negative","margin_top":36}},"promotion_cards":{"type":"promotion-cards","blocks":{"column_1":{"type":"column","settings":{"caption":"20% sale","title":"Suplements","link_label":"Shop Here","link":"","open_new_tab_1":false}},"column_2":{"type":"column","settings":{"caption":"30% sale","title":"Snacks","link_label":"Order Now","link":"","open_new_tab_1":false}},"column_3":{"type